          "prompt_en": "A wide celebrity quote card, brown background, serif light gold \"Stay Hungry, Stay Foolish\", small text \"——Steve Jobs\", a large faint quotation mark in front of the text, character portrait on the left, text on the right, text occupies 2/3 of the picture, character occupies 1/3, character has a gradient transition feeling.",
