          "prompt_zh": "增强这张老图像的分辨率并添加适当的纹理细节，用现代动漫技术重新诠释它。",
          "prompt_en": "Enhance the resolution of this old image and add the appropriate texture details, reinterpreting it with modern anime techniques.",
