          "prompt_zh": "请帮我生成多张 16:9 的涂鸦风格图片，向中学生解释“未来”的概念。图片应采用一致的彩色粗铅笔手绘风格，信息丰富，包含英文文本，使用纯色背景，卡片周围有轮廓，并包含统一的标题，类似于 PowerPoint 演示文稿。",
          "prompt_en": "Help me generate multiple 16:9 doodle-style images to explain the concept of \"futures\" to middle school students. The images should have a consistent colorful, thick-pencil hand-drawn style, be rich in information, feature English text, use solid color backgrounds, have outlines around the cards, and include uniform titles, similar to a PowerPoint presentation.",
