          "id": "std-88",
          "name_zh": "玻璃瓶纪念品",
          "name_en": "Glass Bottle Souvenir",
          "author": "@NanoBanana_labs",
          "source_url": "https://x.com/NanoBanana_labs/status/1967191346017673334",
          "requires_input": true,
          "input_description": "需上传一张参考图像",
          "prompt_zh": "1/7比例的商品化收藏级人偶，以照片中人物为原型，高度写实的风格打造。人偶置于细致的沙滩环境中，沙滩、贝壳和轻柔的海浪交织在一起。整个玩具展示架被封装在一个透明的纪念品玻璃瓶中，使其呈现出高端的微缩立体模型效果，并拥有逼真的光影效果。",
          "prompt_en": "A 1/7 scale commercialized collectible figure of the character from the photo, crafted in a highly realistic style. The figure is placed in a detailed beach environment with sand, seashells, and gentle ocean waves. The entire toy display is enclosed inside a clear souvenir glass bottle, giving it a premium miniature diorama look, with realistic lighting and shadows",
