        {
          "id": "std-90",
          "name_zh": "成为Vtuber",
          "name_en": "Become a Vtuber",
          "author": "@AI_Kei75",
          "source_url": "https://x.com/AI_Kei75/status/1967490141578236329",
          "requires_input": true,
          "input_description": "需上传一张参考图像",
          "prompt_zh": "使用原图创建一个虚拟的Vtuber及其直播画面。\nVtuber的发型和服装将忠实还原原图。\nVtuber的画面为2.5D画质，无需完美还原原图风格，但需要适度的立体感。\nVtuber的表情和姿势可以与原图有所差异。请让Vtuber手持游戏手柄。\n仅将Vtuber的上半身放置在屏幕右下方。将正在游玩的游戏直播画面放置在屏幕中央。将聊天画面放置在屏幕左侧。\n游戏画面的屏幕比例设置为较大，Vtuber的上半身显示较小。\n完全忽略原图的背景和姿势。\n在屏幕的上下添加虚拟的直播平台和浏览器UI。\n生成图像的纵横比与原始图像的纵横比无关。",
          "prompt_en": "Create a fictional Vtuber and their streaming screen using the original image.\nThe Vtuber's hairstyle and clothing will be faithfully reproduced from the original image.\nThe Vtuber image will be 2.5D-like, so it is not necessary to perfectly reproduce the style of the original image. A moderate sense of three-dimensionality is also necessary.\nThe Vtuber's facial expression and pose may be changed from the original image. Have the Vtuber hold a game controller.\nPlace only the Vtuber's upper body in the bottom right of the screen. Place the streaming screen of the game being played in the center of the screen. Place the chat screen on the left side of the screen.\nThe screen ratio is set to a larger size for the game screen, and the upper half of the Vtuber's body is displayed smaller.\nThe background of the original image is completely ignored, as well as the original image pose.\nAdd a fictional streaming platform and browser UI to the top and bottom of the screen.\nThe aspect ratio of the generated image is independent of that of the original image.",
          "variables": [],
          "image_url": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PicoTrex/Awesome-Nano-Banana-images/main/images/case90/output.jpg",
          "tags": [
            "時尚",
            "遊戲",
            "姿態控制",
            "髮型",
            "表情控制"
          ],
          "suggested_scenes": [
            "game",
            "fashion"
          ],
          "difficulty": "intermediate"
        },
        {
          "id": "std-91",
          "name_zh": "车站电影海报",
          "name_en": "Train Station Movie Poster",
          "author": "@AI_Kei75",
          "source_url": "https://x.com/AI_Kei75/status/1967498630467625127",
          "requires_input": true,
          "input_description": "需上传一张参考图像",
          "prompt_zh": "使用原图制作电影海报。电影类型将根据原图的氛围确定。\n无论原图是动画还是真人版，原图的风格和角色设计都将尽可能完美地保留。但姿势和表情可能会根据海报设计进行调整。此外，还可能添加其他人物和物体。\n最终生成的图像将具有照片级真实感。但海报设计除外，因为它将基于原图进行制作。\n海报所贴日本车站地下通道的场景将以逼真的图像进行重现，并添加穿过地下通道的人物。\n海报的反射角度经过调整，使其看起来更加逼真。",
          "prompt_en": "Create a movie poster using the original image. The genre of the movie will be determined based on the atmosphere of the original image.\nRegardless of whether the original image is anime or live-action, the style and character design of the original image will be maintained as perfectly as possible. However, poses and expressions may be changed to match the poster design. Other people and objects may also be added at this time.\nThe final generated image will be photorealistic. This does not apply to the poster design, as it will be based on the original image.\nThe scenery of the underground passage of a Japanese station where the poster is posted will be recreated in a realistic image. People passing through the underground passage will be added.\nThe reflection of the poster is angled to make it look more realistic.",
          "variables": [],
          "image_url": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PicoTrex/Awesome-Nano-Banana-images/main/images/case91/output.jpg",
          "tags": [
            "日式風格",
            "人物",
            "遊戲",
            "電影",
            "姿態控制"
          ],
          "suggested_scenes": [
            "poster",
            "game",
            "photography"
          ],
          "difficulty": "intermediate"
        },
        {
          "id": "std-92",
          "name_zh": "电影休息室",
          "name_en": "Movie Lounge",
          "author": "@tokyo_Valentine",
          "source_url": "https://x.com/tokyo_Valentine/status/1968509703018922082",
          "requires_input": true,
          "input_description": "需上传一张参考图像",
          "prompt_zh": "插画处理：\n背景被去除，角色被转化为手办和周边商品。\n\n主题 / 概述：\n一个逼真的电影院休息区。特别活动主题空间，设在爆米花摊位内，并装饰着角色的世界元素。\n\n地点：\n一个宽敞的电影院爆米花摊。\n有一个收银台，内部有爆米花机。\n有一个饮料柜台，柜台后有售货员。\n收银台上方贴满了正在上映电影的海报。\n\n角色 / 陈列：\n角色扮演者被放置在画面中心。\n手办和亚克力立牌等商品陈列在货架上。\n巨型毛绒玩具和招牌逼真展示。\n设置了电影主题拍照亭，并装饰有角色设计元素。\n\n角色反映的地方：\n当前上映的电影海报。\n联动菜单的弹出广告。\n饮料杯和包装。\n爆米花桶。\n大型 LED LCD 屏。\n\n设计 / 宣传：\n角色插画反映在休息区的每个海报上。\n展示联动食品和饮料的生动视觉效果。\n动画和角色影像投射到 LED 屏上。\n\n摄影角度：\n正面构图。\n强调整个爆米花摊。\n角色扮演者置于中心，周围有商品和广告反映。\n略微低角度拍摄，突显 LED 屏和海报。\n\n画质 / 氛围：\n逼真且细致。\n都市真实光泽感，营造电影院般的氛围和活动感。\n分辨率 4K，长宽比 4:3。",
          "prompt_en": "Illustration Processing:\nThe background is removed and the characters are turned into figurines and merchandise.\nTheme / Overview:\nA photorealistic movie theater lounge. A special event-themed space, set in a popcorn stand, is decorated with the world of the characters.\n\nLocation:\nA spacious popcorn stand in a large movie theater.\nThere is a cash register, with a popcorn machine inside.\nThere is a drink stand with a salesperson behind the counter.\nAbove the register are countless posters of showing movies.\n\nCharacters / Production:\nA character cosplayer is placed in the center of the screen.\nMerchandise such as figurines and acrylic stands are displayed on shelves.\nGiant stuffed animals and signboards are displayed realistically.\nA movie photo booth is set up and decorated with character designs.\n\nPlaces where characters are reflected:\nMovie posters currently being screened.\nPop-up advertisements for the collaboration menu.\nDrink cups and packaging.\nPopcorn buckets.\nLarge LED LCD panel.\n\nDesign / Advertising:\nCharacter illustrations are reflected on each poster in the lounge.\nVivid visuals of the collaboration food and drinks are displayed.\nAnimations and character footage are projected onto LED panels.\n\nCamera Angle:\nComposed from the front.\nEmphasis on the entire popcorn stand.\nA cosplayer is placed in the center, with merchandise and advertisements reflected around them.\nA slightly lower angle captures the LED panels and posters impressively.\n\nQuality / Atmosphere:\nPhotorealistic and detailed depiction.\nAn urban, realistic glossy feel, creating a cinema-like atmosphere with an event-like feel.\nResolution is 4K, aspect ratio is 4:3.",
          "variables": [],
          "image_url": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PicoTrex/Awesome-Nano-Banana-images/main/images/case92/output.jpg",
          "tags": [
            "人物",
            "巨型生物",
            "玩具",
            "毛絨",
            "遊戲"
          ],
          "suggested_scenes": [
            "poster",
            "product",
            "game"
          ],
          "difficulty": "advanced"
        },
        {
          "id": "std-93",
          "name_zh": "切割带有卡通爆炸效果的物体",
          "name_en": "Slice Object with Cartoon Explosion Effect",
          "author": "@Arminn_Ai",
          "source_url": "https://x.com/Arminn_Ai/status/1968375201739177984",
          "requires_input": false,
          "input_description": "",
          "prompt_zh": "将 [OBJECT] 从中间干净利落地切开，上下两半略微分离并悬浮。\n在两半之间，不是自然的内部，而是一个风格化的卡通核爆效果：中心有一根垂直的发光黄橙色气泡烟柱，水平上有一圈宽阔的圆形气泡云冲击波向两侧扩散，冲击波上下带有炽热发光的高光，营造出强烈的热量和能量感。\n[OBJECT] 的外部保持逼真的材质和光照细节，而内部效果高度夸张卡通，形成现实与卡通的强烈对比。工作室灯光，中置构图。",
          "prompt_en": "cut cleanly THE [OBJECT] in half across the middle, the top and bottom halves slightly separated and floating apart.  \nBetween the halves, instead of the natural inside, there is a stylized cartoon nuclear explosion effect: a central vertical column of glowing yellow-orange bubble smoke, with a wide horizontal shockwave ring of round bubbly clouds spreading to the sides, fiery glowing highlights above and below the shockwave, creating the impression of intense heat and energy\nThe outside of the [OBJECT] remains photorealistic with detailed texture and lighting, while the inner effect is highly graphic and playful, giving a striking contrast between realism and cartoon. Studio lighting, centered composition",
          "variables": [
            "[OBJECT]",
            "[OBJECT]"
          ],
          "image_url": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PicoTrex/Awesome-Nano-Banana-images/main/images/case93/case.jpg",
          "tags": [
            "材質",
            "爆炸",
            "切割"
          ],
          "suggested_scenes": [
            "art"
          ],
          "difficulty": "intermediate"
        },
        {
          "id": "std-94",
          "name_zh": "卡通人物主题火车",
          "name_en": "Character-Themed Train",
          "author": "@tokyo_Valentine",
          "source_url": "https://x.com/tokyo_Valentine/status/1968419694920028552",
          "requires_input": true,
          "input_description": "需上传一张参考图像",
          "prompt_zh": "插画处理：\n背景被擦除，角色被转化为手办和周边商品。\n\n主题 / 概述：\n逼真的东京列车内部。整个车厢布置了角色广告和周边商品，打造一个专门为联动活动定制的特殊空间。\n\n角色 / 陈列：\n几名角色扮演者站在画面前景。\n等身板和等身手办展示在列车中部和后部。\n100cm 高的角色手办陈列其中。\n许多角色毛绒玩具排放在空座位上。\n\n广告 / 展示：\n角色插画反映在车厢吊环广告上。\n角色插画展示在列车内部的海报广告上。\n额外安装的 LED 屏上展示角色插画和动画。\n\n插画处理细节：\n背景被擦除，角色转化为手办和周边商品。\n近等身手办、100cm 手办、Q版手办和毛绒玩具被逼真描绘。\n\n摄影角度：\n正面构图，突出列车内部的繁忙氛围。\n前景为角色扮演者的全景镜头，背景为手办、展示板和毛绒玩具。\n低角度拍摄，突出吊环广告和 LED 屏。\n\n画质 / 氛围：\n逼真且细致。\n都市真实光泽感。\n分辨率 4K，长宽比 4:3。",
          "prompt_en": "Illustration Processing:\nThe background is erased and characters are turned into figurines and merchandise.\nTheme / Overview:\nA photorealistic Tokyo train interior. The entire car is decorated with character advertisements and merchandise, creating a special space tailored for a collaboration event.\nCharacters / Production:\nSeveral character cosplayers are standing in the foreground of the screen.\nLife-size panels and life-size figures are displayed in the center and back of the train.\n100cm character figures are on display.\nMany character stuffed toys are lined up in empty seats.\nAdvertising / Display:\nCharacter illustrations are reflected in advertisements on the straps.\nCharacter illustrations are displayed on poster advertisements inside the train.\nCharacter illustrations and animations are displayed on additional LED displays installed inside the train.\nIllustration Processing:\nThe background is erased and characters are turned into figurines and merchandise.\nNear-life-size figures, 100cm figures, deformed figures, and stuffed toys are realistically depicted.\nCamera Angle:\nA frontal composition emphasizes the bustling atmosphere inside the train.\nA large shot of a cosplayer in the foreground, with figures, panels, and stuffed animals in the background.\nA low angle captures the strap advertisements and LED displays impressively.\nQuality / Atmosphere:\nPhotorealistic and detailed depiction.\nAn urban, realistic glossy feel.\nResolution is 4K, aspect ratio is 4:3.",
          "variables": [],
          "image_url": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PicoTrex/Awesome-Nano-Banana-images/main/images/case94/output.jpg",
          "tags": [
            "人物",
            "玩具",
            "毛絨",
            "遊戲",
            "微縮"
          ],
          "suggested_scenes": [
            "poster",
            "product",
            "game"
          ],
          "difficulty": "advanced"
        },
        {
          "id": "std-95",
          "name_zh": "自定义主题公园",
          "name_en": "Custom Theme Park",
          "author": "@AI_Kei75",
          "source_url": "https://x.com/AI_Kei75/status/1968188091237372043",
          "requires_input": true,
          "input_description": "需上传一张参考图像",
          "prompt_zh": "生成一张基于原图的逼真主题公园图像。\n主题公园及其游玩的人物需以极其逼真的风格呈现。白天，阳光明媚。\n色彩方案和设计从原图中提取，并应用于各种设施的色彩和设计上。\n图像中摆放的元素包括：根据原图设计的车辆和建筑、以原图为基础适度夸张的吉祥物服装、印有原图的标牌。\n吉祥物服装设计应以原图为元素，但适度变形以呈现逼真效果。\n人物和吉祥物服装的尺寸必须合理，不得不符合实际比例。\n即使原图是动漫风格，最终生成的图像也必须是逼真的主题公园。务必遵循以上规则。",
          "prompt_en": "Generates a photorealistic theme park image based on the original image.\nThe theme park and the people enjoying it are depicted in an extremely photorealistic style. Daytime. Sunny.\nThe color scheme and design are extracted from the original image and applied to the color scheme and design of various facilities.\nVehicles and buildings based on the original image, mascot costumes that are a distorted version of the original image, and signs with the original image printed on them are placed within the image.\nThe mascot costume design should use the original image as a motif, but be moderately distorted to create a photorealistic look.\nThe sizes of the people and mascot costumes must not be unrealistic.\nEven if the original image is anime-style, the final image must be a photorealistic theme park. Be sure to follow these rules.",
          "variables": [],
          "image_url": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PicoTrex/Awesome-Nano-Banana-images/main/images/case95/output.jpg",
          "tags": [
            "人物",
            "時尚",
            "吉祥物",
            "建築",
            "動漫"
          ],
          "suggested_scenes": [
            "fashion",
            "design",
            "entertainment"
          ],
          "difficulty": "intermediate"
        },
        {
          "id": "std-96",
          "name_zh": "创建星座图",
          "name_en": "Create Constellation Image",
          "author": "@AI_Kei75",
          "source_url": "https://x.com/AI_Kei75/status/1968181164243562665",
          "requires_input": true,
          "input_description": "需上传一张参考图像",
          "prompt_zh": "根据原图创建一幅虚构星座的图像。\n- 星夜背景需逼真，即使原图是动漫风格，也必须呈现逼真的星空效果。\n- 从原图中提取人物、动物或物品，并将其透明置于星空背景上。在此情况下，提取的目标应为单一主题元素（主图案），且仅放置一幅图像。\n- 原图的角色设计、风格和审美需忠实保留，原图背景可忽略。\n- 基于所放置的主题元素，创作一个虚构星座。该星座由约 5 到 10 颗星组成。\n- 分析原图的姿势，将星座的星星合理布置在角色或物体的关键位置。\n- 星座的星星需高亮显示，并用发光线条连接形成星座形态。",
          "prompt_en": "Create an image depicting fictional constellations using the original image as a reference.\n- A photorealistic starry sky. This is maintained even if the original image is anime-style.\n- People, animals, and objects extracted from the original image are placed transparently against the starry sky background. In this case, the extracted target should be a single motif that is the main theme. Also, only one image should be placed.\n- The character design, style, and taste of the original image are faithfully reproduced. The background of the original image can be ignored.\n- An imaginary constellation is created based on the placed motif. This constellation is made up of approximately 5 to 10 stars.\n- The pose of the original image is analyzed, and the stars belonging to the constellation are appropriately positioned in distinctive parts.\n- The stars belonging to the constellation are highlighted, and the stars are connected with glowing lines.",
          "variables": [],
          "image_url": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PicoTrex/Awesome-Nano-Banana-images/main/images/case96/output.jpg",
          "tags": [
            "人物",
            "水晶",
            "遊戲",
            "姿態控制",
            "動漫"
          ],
          "suggested_scenes": [
            "game",
            "design",
            "entertainment"
          ],
          "difficulty": "intermediate"
        },
        {
          "id": "std-97",
          "name_zh": "图片变手机壁纸",
          "name_en": "Turn Image into Phone Wallpaper",
          "author": "@ZHO_ZHO_ZHO",
          "source_url": "https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1967915300063695300",
          "requires_input": true,
          "input_description": "需上传一张参考图像",
          "prompt_zh": "将图片转换为 iPhone 锁屏壁纸效果。手机时间（01:16）、日期（9 月 16 日，星期日）和状态栏详细信息（电池、信号等）叠加显示在图片上，底部显示手电筒和相机图标。原始图片经过调整，以适应加长的智能手机屏幕构图。手机放置在相同配色方案的背景上。",
          "prompt_en": "Transform the image into an iPhone lock screen wallpaper effect. The phone’s time (01:16), date (Sunday, September 16), and status bar details (battery, signal, etc.) appear overlaid on the image, with flashlight and camera icons at the bottom. The original picture is adapted to fit the elongated smartphone screen composition. The phone is placed against a background in the same color scheme.",
          "variables": [],
          "image_url": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PicoTrex/Awesome-Nano-Banana-images/main/images/case97/case.jpg",
          "tags": [
            "壁紙",
            "圖像生成"
          ],
          "suggested_scenes": [
            "art"
          ],
          "difficulty": "intermediate"
        },
        {
          "id": "std-98",
          "name_zh": "制作电影海报",
          "name_en": "Make a Movie Poster",
          "author": "@aiehon_aya",
          "source_url": "https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1967915300063695300",
          "requires_input": true,
          "input_description": "需上传一张参考图像",
          "prompt_zh": "分析上传的照片，检测其中的主体、情绪和氛围。\n自动将照片归类到合适的电影类型（爱情、动作、悬疑、恐怖等）。\n\n根据检测到的类型和氛围，用英文生成以下内容：\n- 电影标题：具有冲击力，符合该类型风格。\n- 短标语 / 宣传语：1–2 行，具有戏剧性或情感渲染。\n- 底部制作信息：包括导演、制片、音乐等虚拟姓名，风格类似真实电影海报。\n- 上映信息：如 “COMING SOON” 或 “In Theaters 2025”。\n\n将上述元素叠加在照片上，呈现电影海报风格：\n- 标题显著展示在中央或下三分之一位置。\n- 标语置于标题上方或下方。\n- 制作信息放在底部，文字较小。\n- 上映信息置于底部中央。\n- 最后添加主演信息，格式固定如下：\n\"Starring: <演员姓名>\"\n\n字体要求：粗体、戏剧性、符合电影类型。\n最终效果应看起来像真实的电影院海报，所有元素与照片的情绪和氛围协调一致。",
          "prompt_en": "Analyze the uploaded photo and detect the subject, mood, and atmosphere.  \nAutomatically classify the photo into a suitable movie genre (romance, action, mystery, horror, etc.).  \n\nBased on the detected genre and mood, generate all the following elements in English:  \n- A cinematic movie title (impactful, authentic to the genre).  \n- A short tagline or catchphrase (1–2 lines, dramatic or emotional).  \n- A credit block at the bottom (with fake names for director, producer, music, etc., styled like real movie posters).  \n- A release note such as “COMING SOON” or “In Theaters 2025.”  \n\nOverlay these elements on the image in a movie-poster style layout:  \n- Place the title prominently in the center or lower third.  \n- Place the tagline above or below the title.  \n- Add a credit block at the bottom in small text.  \n- Add the release note at the bottom center.  \n\nFinally, add the starring section at the bottom, always formatted as:  \n“Starring: ”  \n\nTypography should be bold, dramatic, and genre-appropriate.  \nThe final result must look like a genuine movie poster ready for theaters, with all elements harmonized to the photo’s mood.",
          "variables": [],
          "image_url": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PicoTrex/Awesome-Nano-Banana-images/main/images/case98/output.jpg",
          "tags": [
            "電影",
            "AR",
            "產品攝影",
            "展架",
            "海報"
          ],
          "suggested_scenes": [
            "poster",
            "photography",
            "entertainment"
          ],
          "difficulty": "advanced"
        },
